OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1784054883
OL,3,CMahmood to change law to allow
OL,4,Cdeportation of Rochdale grooming gang
OL,5,Cleader
OL,7,FHome Secretary Shabana Mahmood has
OL,8,Fsaid she will change the law to allow
OL,9,Fthe deportation of a Rochdale grooming
OL,10,Fgang leader.
OL,12,FMs Mahmood announced on Monday that
OL,13,Fshe would change the Immigration and
OL,14,FAsylum Bill, which is passing through
OL,15,Fthe Commons, to remove immunity under
OL,16,Fthe 1971 Immigration Act, which would
OL,17,Fprevent Ahmed from being deported.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1784054883
OL,3,CMahmood to change law to allow
OL,4,Cdeportation of Rochdale grooming gang
OL,5,Cleader
OL,7,FAhmed was released on 2 July after
OL,8,Fserving more than a decade in prison
OL,9,Ffor rape and sexual offences against
OL,10,Fgirls, some as young as 12.
OL,12,FHe had been sentenced to 19 years in
OL,13,Fprison.
OL,15,FKnown to his victims as "Daddy", Ahmed
OL,16,Fhad dual British-Pakistani citizenship
OL,17,Fbut was stripped of his British
OL,18,Fcitizenship following his 2012
OL,19,Fconviction.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1784054883
OL,3,CMahmood to change law to allow
OL,4,Cdeportation of Rochdale grooming gang
OL,5,Cleader
OL,7,FIt came as the government indicated on
OL,8,FMonday that Pakistan could be
OL,9,Fthreatened with visa restrictions
OL,10,Funless it takes back Ahmed.
OL,12,FMs Mahmood admitted in the House of
OL,13,FCommons on Monday that despite the
OL,14,Fpotential law change, she would be
OL,15,Funable to deport him unless Islamabad
OL,16,Fagrees to do so.
OL,18,FSince his release last week, the
OL,19,Fgovernment has been examining ways to
OL,20,Fdeport Ahmed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1784054883
OL,3,CMahmood to change law to allow
OL,4,Cdeportation of Rochdale grooming gang
OL,5,Cleader
OL,7,FThe 1971 law forbids the removal of
OL,8,FCommonwealth citizens who arrived in
OL,9,Fthe UK more than 50 years ago.
OL,11,FThe Home Office said the Bill's powers
OL,12,Fcould also be extended to cover
OL,13,Fterrorists, human trafficking, and
OL,14,Fother violent or dangerous criminals.
OL,16,FMs Mahmood said: "On the subject of
OL,17,Fdeporting foreign criminals, the
OL,18,Fgovernment intends to bring forward an
OL,19,Famendment to this Bill in response to
OL,20,Fthe widely-reported case of the vile
OL,21,Fgrooming gang leader Shabir Ahmed.
OL,26,@xD@ROU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1784054883
OL,3,CMahmood to change law to allow
OL,4,Cdeportation of Rochdale grooming gang
OL,5,Cleader
OL,7,F"Our amendment will provide the Home
OL,8,FSecretary with a new power to disapply
OL,9,FSection 7 of the Immigration Act 1971
OL,10,Ffor serious criminals. This provides
OL,11,Fprotections for long-term UK
OL,12,Fresidents, but clearly should not be
OL,13,Facting as a bar against removal in
OL,14,Fcases like that of Shabir Ahmed.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1784054883
OL,3,CMahmood to change law to allow
OL,4,Cdeportation of Rochdale grooming gang
OL,5,Cleader
OL,7,F"The threshold for this power would be
OL,8,Ftied to the power to deprive
OL,9,Fcitizenship, which applies only in
OL,10,Fcases of exceptional severity. It is
OL,11,Fimportant to note this does not
OL,12,Fguarantee his removal from this
OL,13,Fcountry, those opposite know all too
OL,14,Fwell from their own experience that.
OL,16,F"The Foreign Secretary and I will
OL,17,Fcontinue to work all avenues to pursue
OL,18,Fa deportation."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOUzD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
