OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1784054883
OL,3,CMahmood to change law to allow
OL,4,Cdeportation of Rochdale grooming gang
OL,5,Cleader
OL,7,FThe Bill's second reading was being
OL,8,Fdebated on Monday evening. Amendments
OL,9,Fwould come later in the process at the
OL,10,Fcommittee and report stages.
OL,12,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FChris Philp said the Conservatives
OL,18,Fsupport efforts to remove Ahmed by
OL,19,Fchanging the law.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1784054883
OL,3,CMahmood to change law to allow
OL,4,Cdeportation of Rochdale grooming gang
OL,5,Cleader
OL,7,FBut the shadow home secretary urged
OL,8,Fthe government to consider emergency
OL,9,Flegislation, rather than waiting until
OL,10,Fthe 75-page Immigration and Asylum
OL,11,FBill is agreed.
OL,13,F"There's not a moment to lose and this
OL,14,Fcan quite quickly be fixed," he added.
OL,16,FOn Monday, the Prime Minister's
OL,17,Fofficial spokesman acknowledged that
OL,18,Fchanging the law was only the first
OL,19,Fstep in deporting Ahmed.
OL,26,@uD@AOUvD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
