OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1784054883
OL,3,CMahmood to change law to allow
OL,4,Cdeportation of Rochdale grooming gang
OL,5,Cleader
OL,7,FThe spokesman said: "The country of
OL,8,Forigin must agree to take these vile
OL,9,Fcriminals back and that's why we're
OL,10,Fworking across government to explore
OL,11,Fevery option in this case."
OL,13,FAsked if that included the possibility
OL,14,Fof refusing to issue visas, the
OL,15,Fspokesman said: "I think we've been
OL,16,Fclear that all options remain on the
OL,17,Ftable where countries don't co-operate
OL,18,Fon the return of their nationals."
OL,26,@oD@UOUsD@[O]wD@QOUzD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
