OL,3,CMahmood to change law to allow
OL,4,Cdeportation of Rochdale grooming gang
OL,5,Cleader
OL,7,FPaul Waugh, Labour MP for Rochdale,
OL,8,Ftold the Commons: "Whatever diplomatic
OL,9,Fbarriers exist, they must be
OL,10,Fchallenged.
OL,12,FHe described the "public interest" in
OL,13,Ffavour of deportation as "clear in
OL,14,Fthis case", and added that Ahmed's
OL,15,F"victims were failed for years by the
OL,16,Finstitutions that should have
OL,17,Fprotected them".
OL,26,@pD@SOUtD@ROUtD@bO]uD@ZOUvD@JO]wD@AOUyD@
