OL,3,CMahmood to change law to allow
OL,4,Cdeportation of Rochdale grooming gang
OL,5,Cleader
OL,7,FHe also said: "I can tell you that the
OL,8,Fpeople of Rochdale, whatever their
OL,9,Fracial background, are united in their
OL,10,Fdisgust at paedophiles like Ahmed."
OL,12,FIt is understood that Pakistan is not
OL,13,Fexpected to accept Ahmed.
OL,15,FThe country is reportedly demanding
OL,16,Fthe extradition of two political
OL,17,Fdissidents from the UK to do so.
